                <UserObject label="&amp;nbsp; __init__(config_path: str) → None&lt;br&gt;  load() → List[Actuator]&lt;br&gt;    ← reads config.json actuators section&lt;br&gt;    ← builds ArmController, PumpActuator, AlarmActuator&lt;br&gt;    ← skips disabled actuators&lt;br&gt;  _build_actuator(entry: dict) → Actuator&lt;br&gt;    ← factory method, returns correct subclass&lt;br&gt;  _build_arm(entry: dict) → ArmController&lt;br&gt;    ← builds DHSegment list&lt;br&gt;    ← builds DHSolver&lt;br&gt;    ← returns ArmController&amp;nbsp;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" link="&lt;div class=&quot;relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; aria-label=&quot;python code&quot; role=&quot;group&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;overflow-x-auto&quot;&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);&quot; class=&quot;code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;&quot; class=&quot;language-python&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(211, 215, 222);&quot; class=&quot;token token decorator annotation&quot;&gt;@abstractmethod&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 123, 244);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(112, 184, 255);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;infer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(211, 215, 222);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(211, 215, 222);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; frame&lt;/span&gt;&lt;spa