                <UserObject label="&lt;span&gt;  activate() → None&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← opens pump GPIO pin&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← records _start_time&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  deactivate() → None&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← closes pump GPIO pin&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  is_healthy() → bool&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← checks GPIO pin state&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  _safety_cutoff() → None&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ← auto deactivates if running &amp;gt; max_duration_s&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;" link="&lt;div class=&quot;relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; aria-label=&quot;python code&quot; role=&quot;group&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;overflow-x-auto&quot;&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);&quot; class=&quot;code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;&quot; class=&quot;language-python&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(211, 215, 222);&quot; class=&quot;token token decorator annotation&quot;&gt;@abstractmethod&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 123, 244);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(112, 184, 255);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;infer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(211, 215, 222);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(211, 215, 222);&quot; class=&quot;token token&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; frame&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;col